  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package was signed on 2026-03-01 and subsequently updated post-signing to incorporate a supplemental mesh-refinement validation result dated 2026-03-22. The updated evidence was appended without re-signing the package, introducing a future-dated evidence artefact relative to the recorded signatureTimestamp. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at Model Risk Level 5.",
