      "description": "A supplemental grid-convergence index (GCI) study was completed after the package was signed to address reviewer comments on discretization error. Three mesh levels (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.3M cells) were evaluated; GCI values below 2.1% confirm mesh-independent hemolysis predictions. This result was appended to the package post-signing without re-signing; the evidenceTimestamp reflects the actual date of study completion.",
